{"tid":389752,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"［超數碼暴龍機］透明綠、透明紫同4.5比較","createTime":"2017-09-06T13:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T03:45:53.000Z","uid":25652,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e7804928e4498b023ccbc69de3295c48dfd54b","tid":389752,"uid":25652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-06T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"港版特別版透明綠同透明紫超1.5？聽人講就聽得多，可惜真機就真係見都未見過。<br />\n<br />\n原本諗住呢世人都會帶住呢個遺憾，又點會估到有緣成功收集到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去圖啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/213822_dabd486b8328dfefc9e3b3173d0fab83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F213822_dabd486b8328dfefc9e3b3173d0fab83.jpg&h=8aa94d72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記住透明綠同透明紫1.5 一定係符合呢幾點：<br />\n<br />\n1. 係港版盒，有繁體字嘅貼紙<br />\n<br />\n2. 透明綠隻色比4.5淺，無咁實<br />\n<br />\n3. 按鈕色都係唔同！4.5隻黃色係濃啲實啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n肉眼睇係睇到有分別，但影出黎又好似無乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位可以留意下按鈕嘅色，係有分別的。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/06/213826_0f77c57838ffb59e1cd3c98955f307c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F06%2F213826_0f77c57838ffb59e1cd3c98955f307c8.jpg&h=ce258426&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa4a9a05421e9c267df0541deda3e91694346084","tid":389752,"uid":17543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"推"}]}